public final class ToStringComparator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<java.lang.Object>, java.io.Serializable

Compares two object instances just by invoking Object.toString() on them and then compares the strings.

There is no need to create dedicated instances of this class. Just use the existing INSTANCE.
